<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ - HigherCareer System</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/logo.ico">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/faq.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("../includes/nav") %>

    <div class="faq-container">
        
        <div class="title">
            <h2>‚ùì Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Find answers to common questions about the HigherCareer system, or <a href="#">contact our support</a></p>

            <div class="search">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
    
                <input type="search" name="search" id="search"  placeholder="Search ...">
            </div>
        </div>




        <main class="main-content">
            <section class="faq-section">
                <div class="faq-item" data-expanded="false">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How do I add a new student?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>To add a new student, go to the "Manage Students" section, click on "Add Student," and fill out the required details.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-expanded="false">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How can I view fee collection details?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Navigate to the "Fee Management" section to view details on collected and pending fees.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-expanded="false">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How do I reset my password?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Go to your profile settings and click "Reset Password." Follow the instructions to update your password securely.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-expanded="false">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How do I generate student reports?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>To generate reports, go to "Student Reports" and choose the type of report (academic or attendance). You can customize filters as needed.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h4>Still can't find your answer?</h4>
                <p class="happy">We are happy to help</p>
                <button><i class="fa-solid fa-message"></i> Chat with us</button>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
    <%- include("../includes/footer.ejs") %>
    <script src="/js/faq.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
